Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.05,0:01:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.09,0:01:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小…小夜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.93,0:02:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 你的背…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.50,0:02:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好暖和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.31,0:02:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.88,0:02:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 能遇見你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.58,0:02:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.25,0:02:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小夜 小夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.36,0:02:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.53,0:02:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第七十五話\N最後的聖戰  兩個天翔龍閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.96,0:03:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.57,0:03:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他失明了\N還想跟翔伍大人交手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.94,0:03:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要打倒我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.34,0:03:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用天翔龍閃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.48,0:03:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣你應該會注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.15,0:03:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,此時除了投降之外\N沒別的方法可以救人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.03,0:03:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第11部隊做好攻擊準備了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.43,0:03:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次攻擊要殲滅敵人半數
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.44,0:03:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.97,0:03:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開我 可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.87,0:03:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要我說幾次你們才懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.04,0:04:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村現在正在說服天草翔伍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.34,0:04:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們停止攻擊呀\N不停止的話我就咬人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.72,0:04:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個女孩是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.62,0:04:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不知道緋村的力量嗎\N他是傳說中的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.09,0:04:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是阻止了志志雄真實的人哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.19,0:04:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帶走她 把她關起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.33,0:04:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開我 這個石頭腦袋 可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.90,0:04:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准你們再碰那位小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.65,0:04:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愛爾思坦先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.58,0:04:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愛爾思坦領事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.38,0:04:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是來警告的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.32,0:04:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你們立刻撤回\N對那個山丘上的人的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.83,0:04:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們現在的行為\N是不可原諒的野蠻行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.36,0:04:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要你們立刻停止攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.50,0:05:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恕我失禮 您是荷蘭領事\N來這裏有什麼理由嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.57,0:05:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您以為您有權利命令我們嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.28,0:05:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們從江戶以前\N到現在的明治時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.65,0:05:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幾百年來\N虐待殘殺天主教徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.22,0:05:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您不可能不曉得我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.52,0:05:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,西洋諸國對這種\N不人道的鎮壓的責難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.22,0:05:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.09,0:05:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不光是我的祖國荷蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.60,0:05:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美國、英國、法國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.53,0:05:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都對這個國家\N對有信仰的人的蓄意迫害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.61,0:05:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有著強烈的批評
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.51,0:05:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在\N你們明知會招來更大的反感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.11,0:05:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不顧一切\N要攻擊神的信徒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.95,0:05:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.22,0:05:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們再屠殺的話\N可是會引來西方列強責難哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.96,0:05:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,荷蘭、英國可能會貿易制裁\N搞不好發展成戰爭哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.06,0:06:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們想不顧後果\N一意孤行下去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.80,0:06:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 天草翔伍\N是想製造內亂的暴徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.90,0:06:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是信仰問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.77,0:06:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的目的是粉碎他的陰謀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.94,0:06:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是我在說的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.41,0:06:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村劍心一定會\N讓天草翔伍投降的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.05,0:06:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也相信緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.78,0:06:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也聽過那出名的維新志士\N緋村的名字吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.95,0:06:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要他能和平解決事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.96,0:06:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們沒有理由再攻擊村人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.29,0:06:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愛爾思坦先生\N您說的話確實有理 但…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.96,0:06:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.70,0:06:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不接受外人干涉內政
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.04,0:06:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叛徒必需全體處死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.11,0:06:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.24,0:06:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只給一個小時時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.38,0:06:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一小時以內\N天草翔伍不表明完全投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.25,0:06:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就開始總攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.19,0:07:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道嗎 一小時後總攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.53,0:07:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.66,0:07:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做好萬全準備\N把他們全部殺死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.84,0:07:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒在一個小時內說服他\N所有人都會被殺死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.41,0:07:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在只能\N把希望寄托在緋村身上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.82,0:07:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.99,0:07:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.49,0:07:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要決鬥啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.49,0:07:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決鬥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.42,0:07:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟翔伍大人決鬥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.16,0:07:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個人觸怒大人而失明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.06,0:07:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受過神之子制裁的人\N怎麼這麼大膽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.94,0:07:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要叫我跟他們投降？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.52,0:08:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任何人都不能侮辱我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.49,0:08:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神聖的死亡\N才是有尊嚴的選擇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.40,0:08:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要引導我選上的子民\N到幸福的天堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.33,0:08:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是你的真心話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.24,0:08:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.08,0:08:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不可思議呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.54,0:08:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看不到你的臉與表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.18,0:08:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 這樣讓我反而…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.65,0:08:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以看到你的內心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.15,0:08:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那雷鳴的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.02,0:08:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刀劍交鋒的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.96,0:08:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那天晚上你的飛天御劍流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.90,0:08:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確實是名符其實的天上之劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.74,0:08:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,達到了劍法的最大極限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.40,0:08:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下你的一劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.94,0:09:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我感受到無法言喻的顫動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.08,0:09:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.38,0:09:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那極限的一劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.41,0:09:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,證明了你的身與心\N都已窮盡御劍流的奧義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.69,0:09:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,御劍流的奧義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.79,0:09:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是救人 保護人\N那熾熱的心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.77,0:09:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你應該是每奪走一個人的命\N就胸口流下血淚的男人吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.11,0:09:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算你奪走的是\N你恨極了的敵人的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.98,0:09:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算你再怎樣保持冷靜理智
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.52,0:09:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奪走人命的那一瞬間\N你的心底會掙扎痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.92,0:09:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不這樣的話 你是不可能\N把御劍流練到極限的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.69,0:09:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你這樣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.56,0:09:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帶領仰慕自己\N跟隨自己的88個人赴死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.60,0:09:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你絕不可能覺得幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.20,0:10:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的心\N應該是被悲傷給凍結了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.05,0:10:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.28,0:10:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想說你也承受過\N同樣的掙扎與痛苦是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.35,0:10:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,背負著不得不奪走\N眾多生命的宿命的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.99,0:10:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我不能放著你不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.54,0:10:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.17,0:10:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧 我必需跟你做\N飛天御劍流最後的決戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.22,0:10:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要自己決定\N自己命終的時刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.66,0:10:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天是聖靈之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.66,0:10:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要跟88個信徒一同戰鬥\N然後升天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.53,0:11:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最了餞別這最後的奇跡\N我要打敗你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.45,0:11:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去聖靈之丘一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.01,0:11:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等劍心一成功說服翔伍他們\N我立刻就升起烽火當信號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.75,0:11:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到山丘上烽火升起\N馬上阻止軍隊的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.32,0:11:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.18,0:11:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始了\N最後的戰鬥終於開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.21,0:11:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心在這場戰鬥中\N打敗天草翔伍的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.75,0:11:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷龍閃的封印就會解除\N劍心的眼睛就能復明瞭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.95,0:12:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是阿薰\N劍心打算怎樣打敗天草翔伍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.79,0:12:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他怎樣克服\N眼睛失明的缺點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.50,0:12:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道 但劍心應該有辦法\N洞察交手過的敵人的動向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.44,0:12:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且對手使用的是他\N熟到不能再熟的飛天御劍流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.38,0:12:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.24,0:12:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.08,0:12:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我感覺到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.18,0:12:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那兩個人好像交手越久\N心底深處的某種東西越相通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.35,0:12:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,某種東西相通嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.69,0:12:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是御劍流的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.26,0:12:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不經由語言 經由劍招往來\N瞭解彼此的某種東西…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.14,0:12:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接招吧 緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.02,0:13:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.09,0:13:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下了\N他以雙龍閃接下雙龍閃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.63,0:13:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這男人讀出我的行動了\N而且比那天晚上更快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.44,0:13:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你受傷了…被打傷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.77,0:13:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這跟你無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.82,0:13:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翔伍大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.52,0:13:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那男人失明了\N還跟翔伍大人平手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.46,0:13:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是翔伍大人的反應很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.40,0:13:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你果然被打傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.46,0:13:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不趕快治療的話你會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.60,0:13:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒那個必要 我是神子\N不需要你人類的智慧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.68,0:14:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還自稱是神嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.88,0:14:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幼時父母被殘酷殺死的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.05,0:14:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以為自己不變成神\N人們就無法得到拯救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.39,0:14:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才下那個決心要成為神\N這樣說服自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.53,0:14:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,支撐自己過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.50,0:14:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.27,0:14:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.81,0:14:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是事實違反你堅決的意願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.54,0:14:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你深深為\N無法成為神的自己而苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.91,0:14:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何你無法治好妹妹的病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.25,0:14:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何…無法救她的命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.66,0:14:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想至少要保住你唯一的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.79,0:14:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是在天國 而是在人間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.60,0:14:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想讓妹妹跟村人們\N都可以獲得幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.33,0:15:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現實卻是\N你在斷送所愛的人們的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.14,0:15:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此你激烈地責備自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.71,0:15:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你應該已經注意到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.94,0:15:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是神 你只是一個\N煩惱、痛苦的脆弱的凡人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.32,0:15:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把自己當成一個普通人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.49,0:15:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為那些崇拜你的人\N重新開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.24,0:15:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翔伍啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.61,0:15:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是你最後一次來見我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.85,0:15:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奪走我的視力之後\N你一直痛苦不已的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.99,0:15:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看見你的善良與苦惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.29,0:16:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底想背著重擔\N以神自居到什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.06,0:16:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到我領導被欺壓的人們\N得到幸福為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.74,0:16:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之前我要以天上之劍\N天翔龍閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.87,0:16:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給骯髒的人們施加洗禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.48,0:16:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你這樣聰明的男人\N為什麼還想不通呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.78,0:16:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是以憎恨為糧食\N得到天翔龍閃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.19,0:16:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的劍招\N被憎恨的烏雲所覆蓋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.69,0:16:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的天翔龍閃\N遲早會被破解掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.90,0:16:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村 看是你說的話正確\N還是真實屬於我……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.08,0:16:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確認的方法只有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.18,0:16:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,答案就在天翔龍閃之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.31,0:16:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要以我的天翔龍閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.75,0:16:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破解你的天翔龍閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.00,0:17:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要使出天翔龍閃了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.84,0:17:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.21,0:17:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩個天翔龍閃要衝突了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.78,0:17:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是你自己的決定 去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.12,0:17:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你了 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.55,0:17:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翔伍…翔伍就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.13,0:17:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要把意念\N灌注在這把逆刃刀裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.14,0:18:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翔伍 你要變強啊 拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.65,0:18:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是將來要領導許多人的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.25,0:18:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拋棄這小小的悲傷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.56,0:18:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要成為神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.53,0:18:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成為神再回來這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.56,0:18:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了保護被欺壓的人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.10,0:18:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過去我到底是為何而戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.97,0:19:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對無可取代的人揮劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.04,0:19:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻放掉最重要的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.59,0:19:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連憎恨這念頭都不曉得\N那幸福的時光…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.03,0:19:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從那時候開始到現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.33,0:19:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我到底拋棄了什麼\N又遺忘了什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.23,0:19:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時光再也無法倒流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.61,0:19:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.13,0:19:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村 讓我死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.70,0:20:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我…死吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.78,0:20:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有保護我所愛的人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.42,0:20:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我並不是神 只是個凡人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.49,0:20:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要死 翔伍大人 別死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.06,0:20:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別丟下我們呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.14,0:20:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翔伍大人 翔伍大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.34,0:20:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過去翔伍大人一直保護我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.61,0:20:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可以只有我們得救…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.68,0:20:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求求你 不要那麼說呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.92,0:20:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論天涯海角\N我們都要跟翔伍大人一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.15,0:20:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再也找不到像翔伍大人\N這麼好心的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.86,0:20:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請當我這個老人的支柱吧\N像過去那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.66,0:21:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有翔伍大人的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.26,0:21:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道\N怎樣去尋找幸福的國度呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.93,0:21:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請為我們創造幸福的國度吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.87,0:21:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為我們創造吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.34,0:21:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為我們創造吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.74,0:21:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.87,0:21:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你 翔伍大人 翔伍大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.58,0:21:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家…大家都是\N這麼仰慕翔伍大人的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.26,0:21:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要永遠保護大家哦\N我們約定好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.77,0:21:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這麼約定？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.77,0:21:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 我答應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.45,0:21:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.88,0:21:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.25,0:22:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你眼睛可以看見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.09,0:22:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以看見了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.19,0:22:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩 我可以看見你的臉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.36,0:22:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了 太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.27,0:22:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直都相信劍心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.74,0:22:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.95,0:22:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇跡發生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.95,0:22:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是劍心創造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.09,0:22:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對\N創造奇跡的是人們的關懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.43,0:22:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天草翔伍終於恢復成人了

